<li><a href="http://colsearch.nfsa.afc.gov.au/nfsa/search/summary/summary.w3p;adv=yes;group=;groupequals=;page=0;parentid=;query=Number%3A677631%20|%20Number%3A677630%20|%20Number%3A677629%20|%20Number%3A677627%20|%20Number%3A677011%20|%20Number%3A676406%20|%20Number%3A676405%20|%20Number%3A675872%20|%20Number%3A674761%20|%20Number%3A671223%20|%20Number%3A671176%20|%20Number%3A671153%20|%20Number%3A671145%20|%20Number%3A671133;querytype=;resCount=10" class="external text" title="http://colsearch.nfsa.afc.gov.au/nfsa/search/summary/summary.w3p;adv=yes;group=;groupequals=;page=0;parentid=;query=Number%3A677631%20|%20Number%3A677630%20|%20Number%3A677629%20|%20Number%3A677627%20|%20Number%3A677011%20|%20Number%3A676406%20|%20Number%3A676405%20|%20Number%3A675872%20|%20Number%3A674761%20|%20Number%3A671223%20|%20Number%3A671176%20|%20Number%3A671153%20|%20Number%3A671145%20|%20Number%3A671133;querytype=;resCount=10" rel="nofollow">Theatre of the Mind</a> at the National Film and Sound Archive.</li>
<li><a href="http://natf.org/" class="external text" title="http://natf.org/" rel="nofollow">The Well-tempered Audio Dramatist</a> Treatise on writing, producing, performing and directing audio plays in the 21st century.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.wirelesstheatrecompany.co.uk" class="external text" title="http://www.wirelesstheatrecompany.co.uk" rel="nofollow">The Wireless Theatre Company</a> Modern day radio drama for download to iPods.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.voiceacting.co.uk" class="external text" title="http://www.voiceacting.co.uk" rel="nofollow">Voiceacting.co.uk</a> Online amateur radio drama resources.</li>
<li><a href="http://radioplayinsrilanka.blogspot.com/" class="external text" title="http://radioplayinsrilanka.blogspot.com/" rel="nofollow">Sinhala Radio Plays</a> Radio Play resources from Sri Lanka</li>
</ul>


